## FAQ

**How do I get testnet ETH?**
Visit faucet.quicknode.com and select Base Sepolia.

**What is BHNK?**
BHNK is the BhanksToken — the utility and governance token of this protocol.

**Are the contracts audited?**
No. These contracts are for educational purposes. Use at your own risk.

**How do I connect my wallet?**
Click the Connect Wallet button. Coinbase Wallet and MetaMask are supported.